        <h2 class="font_2 c_primary" style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Generated <code>:root</code> snippet</h2>
        <p class="reading-typography font-size_down" style="margin-top: 0;">While you adjust controls, this page applies the same tokens on <code>:root</code> (via <code>&lt;html&gt;</code> inline properties) so Arches utilities pick them up. The snippet begins with <strong>static</strong> Google Fonts <code>&lt;link&gt;</code> tags (preconnect + one stylesheet per chosen family) suitable for pasting into a CMS or <code>&lt;head&gt;</code> include, then your <code>:root</code> <code>&lt;style&gt;</code>. System state colors match the current defaults in <code>_includes/annual/root.html</code>.</p>
        <pre><code id="brandThemeOutput"></code></pre>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary brand-gen__copy" id="brandThemeCopy">Copy to clipboard</button>
